song.title: No Submission
song.lyrics:
No Submission Lyrics[Verse 1]
Shut out, cut out
Bloodless, hopeless
Hating as I fade
Pulsate, pushing
Head exploding
Razor-sharp, the tong is

Put down, run out
I could care less
Throw down as I hate
Feeding, needing
Severed, bleeding
Pull it out, exposing
[Verse 2]
Take a beating
Needle speeding
Fall into a daze
Defecation, detonation
Tear the tong apart and
Terminate it, suffocate it
Spitting in your face
Accelerate, exterminate it
Take it all in hand

[Chorus]
There's no submission
No submission
